OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"They did everything they could
OL,7,Fpossibly do": Deputy Chief Constable
OL,8,Fof Derbyshire Police Simon Blatchly
OL,9,Fpraises the conduct of officers.
OL,11,FThe Deputy Chief Constable of
OL,12,FDerbyshire Police says he is
OL,13,F"immensely proud" of the way his
OL,14,Fofficers conducted themselves before
OL,15,Fthe shooting of an armed knifeman in
OL,16,F2022.
