OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,FHis comments came after a jury found
OL,7,FMarius Ciolac, who was fatally shot by
OL,8,Fa firearms officer after brandishing a
OL,9,Fknife in a police station car park,
OL,10,Fwas lawfully killed.
OL,12,FCiolac was shot in the abdomen outside
OL,13,FAscot Drive police station in Derby on
OL,14,Fthe morning of October 7th 2022, after
OL,15,Fentering the compound holding a blade,
OL,16,Fand a cat in a pet carrier bag.
