OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,FDerby Coroners Court heard that Mr
OL,7,FCiolac, a 35-year-old builder who was
OL,8,Foriginally from Romania, smashed
OL,9,Fthrough the first layer of the
OL,10,Fstation's double glazed windows with
OL,11,Fthe knife, appeared to "lick" the
OL,12,Fblade at officers through the door,
OL,13,Fand hit police cars before the two
OL,14,Farmed officers arrived.
OL,26,@sD@XOUsD@]O]
