OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Simon Blatchly
OL,7,Fsaid: "The tragic set of circumstances
OL,8,Fthat took place on 7 October 2022, at
OL,9,FAscot Drive have had a long-lasting
OL,10,Feffect on all those involved.
OL,12,F"And, following the conclusion of the
OL,13,Finquest into Mr Ciolac's death, my
OL,14,Fthoughts and condolences remain with
OL,15,Fhis family and friends.
OL,17,F"As was heard during the three weeks
OL,18,Fof evidence and witness testimony, the
OL,19,Fsituation that was faced that day was
OL,20,Funprecedented.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
