OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"Officers take an oath to protect
OL,7,Flife, and they did all they could to
OL,8,Fprotect themselves, their colleagues,
OL,9,Fthe public and, ultimately, Mr Ciolac.
OL,11,FHe continued "Having seen the footage
OL,12,Ffrom the incident, it is clear that
OL,13,Fsignificant attempts were made to
OL,14,Fnegotiate with Mr Ciolac and bring the
OL,15,Fincident to a safe conclusion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
