OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"They had attempted to use Taser, with
OL,7,Fno effect, and as he attempted to
OL,8,Fsmash his way into the station, the
OL,9,Fdecision was made that, due to the
OL,10,Frisk posed, armed officers had to be
OL,11,Fdeployed.
OL,13,F"When officers arrived, they used a
OL,14,Fstun grenade and a baton round in a
OL,15,Ffurther attempt to use all the less
OL,16,Flethal options to stop Mr Ciolac.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
