OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"However, for reasons that remain
OL,7,Funclear, within 20 seconds of armed
OL,8,Fofficers walking into the car park at
OL,9,FAscot Drive, Mr Ciolac rushed towards
OL,10,Fone of the officers armed with a
OL,11,Fknife, leaving him with no other
OL,12,Foption than to fire his weapon.
OL,14,F"Once Mr Ciolac was restrained,
OL,15,Fofficers immediately began to
OL,16,Fundertake first aid and paramedics
OL,17,Fwere on the scene in a matter of
OL,18,Fminutes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@IO]
