OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,FMr Blatchly said the use of a firearm
OL,7,Fby an officer in Derbyshire is an
OL,8,F"extremely rare event".
OL,10,FHe said "That small number is
OL,11,Ftestament to the high bar set for the
OL,12,Fuse of a firearm, and the extensive
OL,13,Ftraining that is undertaken by
OL,14,Fofficers to resolve matters through
OL,15,Fless lethal means.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@VO]rD@IOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
