OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"When an incident of this nature takes
OL,7,Fplace, there is rightly a robust
OL,8,Finvestigation undertaken by the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,Fwhich, after reviewing footage and the
OL,11,Fstatements by all those at the scene,
OL,12,Ffound that the force used by the
OL,13,Fofficers, including the officer who
OL,14,Fdischarged their firearm, was
OL,15,Fproportionate.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
