OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1739559020
OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"All the officers who ran towards
OL,7,Fdanger on that Friday morning were
OL,8,Fclear that they had to protect their
OL,9,Fcolleagues, the public and try, to the
OL,10,Fbest of their abilities, to ensure
OL,11,Fthat Mr Ciolac did not come to harm.
OL,13,F"While they understand the risks that
OL,14,Ftheir roles may place them in ` it
OL,15,Fdoes not mean that they do not feel
OL,16,Ffear"
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
