OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"While they understand they will
OL,7,Fattend potentially dangerous
OL,8,Fincidents, this was unlike anything
OL,9,Fthat many had been exposed to ` and
OL,10,Fthe impact has been significant.
OL,12,F"Those officers, as well as civilian
OL,13,Fstaff inside the building, are not
OL,14,Frobots, they are mothers, fathers,
OL,15,Fhusbands, wives, sisters and brothers.
OL,16,FAnd while they understand the risks
OL,17,Fthat their roles may place them in `
OL,18,Fit does not mean that they do not feel
OL,19,Ffear.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
