OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"I am immensely proud of the manner in
OL,7,Fwhich they conducted themselves that
OL,8,Fday and their attempts, at serious
OL,9,Frisk to themselves, to bring the
OL,10,Fincident to a safe conclusion and we
OL,11,Fwill continue to support those
OL,12,Fofficers and staff affected."
