OL,3,CPolice boss praises officers' conduct
OL,4,Cbefore shooting of armed knifeman
OL,6,F"During the course of the police
OL,7,Finteractions with Mr Ciolac, he
OL,8,Frepeatedly ignored instructions to
OL,9,Fdrop the knife and officers initially
OL,10,Ftried to resolve the threat using
OL,11,Fvarious forms of non-lethal force,
OL,12,Fwhich were ultimately unsuccessful.
OL,14,F"The officer who fired the fatal shot
OL,15,Fsaid he feared for his life as Mr
OL,16,FCiolac ran towards him while holding a
OL,17,Fknife, and his account was
OL,18,Fcorroborated by the extensive CCTV and
OL,19,Fpolice body worn footage reviewed by
OL,20,Four investigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
